The final result for the $\alpha=+1$ fermions is therefore
\begin{eqnarray}
	&& \frac{1}{2}\sum_{E\,\in\,\mathds{Z}+\frac{1}{2}}e^{-\mu|E|}\left(\Omega^+_E+\Omega^+_{-E}\right)=
